Active Items
    -Rail gun -> Shoots laser that does damage
    -Missile Barrage -> Spawns Enemy tracking missiles
    -EMP -> Stuns enemies around you temporarily
    -Hack -> Hacks an enemy mech to your team (Charm)
    - .... -> Heal x ammount
