Combo Items
    -Extends Punch Combo by 1 (until 4 or 5)
    -Extends Kick Combo by 1 (until 4 or 5)

    -Extends Airborne Punch Combo by 1 (until 4 or 5)
    -Extends Airborne Kick Combo by 1 (until 4 or 5)

